room_title: Escape room "Pirate Treasure" by Escape on Main in St. Louis
room_address: 340 North Main Street Ste 205 Saint Charles, MO 63301
room_description:
You are captured by the infamous Captain RedBeard.  While docked you managed to escape the shackles.  Now it is your turn for payback!  

The Captain and his crew are out getting supplies and will be back in 60 minutes.  It is your mission to find and steal the Captain's legendary treasure and escape for good!
